{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14605/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14605"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:46:05"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["backlighting"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man walks around a dance hall's second floor balcony."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14605","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14605"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1/f4c1d11b-de1a-4df1-870c-922efff0c1c1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T20:02:24.930Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds’s dark, almost featureless silhouette stands out against the brightly lit, colorful scene of the party. Unlike the others on the balcony with him, no color is visible on his form, and he is alone, not part of a couple. This choice shows his isolation from the party—he does not, or at least feels he does not, belong here, and cannot become a full participant in the celebration.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:781.6771994426754,208.58628582802544,903.2424363057326,340.4155055732483"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1/e5061216-d898-4c0e-b9ba-4d729cdc0344","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T20:03:12.697Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>After chaos breaks out on the dance floor and Reynolds loses sight of Alma (his light, his joy), the spotlight turns away from Reynolds, dropping casting him in darkness once again.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14605/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:538.5213475318471,179.4446656050955